data.title: Kino Tuškanac
data.text:
CAST:

Christopher Lambert,

Eddy Mitchell,

Agnčs Soral

SCRIPT:

Marco Ferreri,

Didier Kaminka,

Enrico Oldoini

Synopsis:

All the women handsome Michael meets have one flaw: they lack total commitment. Eventually Michael finds one worth loving – persomified in an electrical key chain shaped as a woman’s head that keeps repeating "I love you".
